| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1081 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 42ac12d5-ee25-5a53-9824-b0c00467af2e"
